From e9e29f870a0c3d9c0d27bc1e11b94cd8b42a1916 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Thierry Reding <treding@nvidia.com>
Date: Thu, 31 Jul 2025 18:18:02 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 100/138] arm64: tegra: Remove numa-node-id properties

These were initially added because some software was checking for their
presence. However, the device is not NUMA, so adding these is wrong and
hence they should be removed.

