From fa7b97b404ce4574d2cca1716b03629a607d5bf9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Prathamesh Shete <pshete@nvidia.com>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 13:42:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 112/138] pinctrl: tegra: Export tegra_pinctrl_probe()

